{"tid":1103180,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"寫左個免費生意買賣平台","createTime":"2019-04-12T08:34:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T03:20:44.000Z","uid":85519,"like":13,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1a0cb8b3da171e68e695ab5f11d489ced75a7d95","tid":1103180,"uid":85519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T08:34:12.000Z","msg":"自己寫左隻app做生意買賣嘅platform (暫時得 android)<br />\n<br />\n隻app入面會gather唔同生意嘅賣盤, 每當有新盤都會出push alert比所有users。<br />\n每個賣盤都會有個chatroom, 可以比有興趣嘅買家問問題。潛在買家亦可以直接PM賣家。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=easybiz.kh.easybiz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Deasybiz.kh.easybiz&d=%2FAErJKvlI7yUl6Jkpxfv8AZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=e4910b4e\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=easybiz.kh.easybiz</a><br />\n<br />\n隻app係免費嘅，無論係出post, 用chatroom同pm。本身諗住pm會收費，例如每次request pm都收~$20左右。不過暫時同係keep住免費，如果server費太高可能會改。<br />\n<br />\n因為唔係用咗好多時間寫，如果有問題或者意見可以話我知。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/double_deedee\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fdouble_deedee&d=%2FAErJKvlI7yUl6Jkpxfv8AZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=9aac8a46\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/double_deedee</a>"},{"pid":"3430e1e736e262a01e9c61ad3125b91ea0a005a3","tid":1103180,"uid":53194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T08:37:46.000Z","msg":"正評加油<br />\n<br />\n好過果D有IDEA 搵人夾寫APP"},{"pid":"c876fbdf74c45b43cf60df2fc45b605a1a81bd4e","tid":1103180,"uid":85519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3430e1e736e262a01e9c61ad3125b91ea0a005a3","tid":1103180,"uid":53194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T08:37:46.000Z","msg":"正評加油<br />\n<br />\n好過果D有IDEA 搵人夾寫APP"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T08:43:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fd7ed08bf118a5c24453a748351ff5b55b70417","tid":1103180,"